        "easy": [
            `<h2 style="font-size: 1.2em;">Facing Challenges with Christ's Strength</h2>
            <p>Have you ever faced something really hard and felt like giving up? Remember, Philippians 4:13 says, "I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me." This means that with Jesus' help, you can overcome any obstacle. Think about a time when you needed to be brave, like speaking in front of the class or trying a new sport. With faith and prayer, you can find the courage to succeed. Always believe that Jesus is with you, giving you the strength you need.</p>`
